When no mode is found, `FirstOrDefault` returns the default value "websocket", which doesn't have the "mode=" prefix. The subsequent `Replace("mode=", "")` on line 228 won't have any effect. This should be:

```csharp
var mode = pluginParts.FirstOrDefault(t => t.StartsWith("mode="));
var modeValue = mode?.Replace("mode=", "") ?? "websocket";
```
